Empath::

Sensing the presence of the famed Ultra Magnus in the base is too 
much of a temptation for Empath to pass up, and she plans her arrival 
time so she'll get there just as Magnus answers the question.  She 
knows her Decepticon insignia carries some shock value, especially to 
an old arch-enemy.
